{"tid":840993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭妹全裸躺高速公路　稱「尋找愛情」釀大塞車","createTime":"2018-09-29T08:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T09:14:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":346,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"a85a8946a7aa1a82dd9bf6dbc1e484e2933fe07f","tid":840993,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"一名烏克蘭妹全裸躺在高速公路上，造成大塞車，民眾報警後到場問她為何要這樣做，她表示「正在尋找愛情」。據白俄羅斯《Gazeta Slonimskaya》報導，9月21日11點左右，烏克蘭基輔有一名女子，全裸躺在聖西里爾教堂(St. Cyril's Monastery)前方的高速公路上，引起了大塞車。起初，該女子只是躺著，用雙手蓋住乳房，但是過了一陣子後，她起車試圖打開經過的轎車車門，不過她沒有成功，後來她改為爬上轎車的車頂，而駕駛也因此報了警。 警方跟醫療人員趕到現場後，她向前來的人說，她正在用這種方式「尋找愛情」，而她試圖攔下的車輛，看來就是她相中的「白馬王子」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"b7d6ea27f19d16bc806caf6115fd8f5211538261","tid":840993,"uid":58140,"like":2751,"dislike":11,"score":2740,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"我唔撚數啦 直接屌你老母"},{"pid":"55774356435690a6a3cb4e499871df640475c062","tid":840993,"uid":4826,"like":98,"dislike":3,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"網絡孤島"},{"pid":"6532519facaf64d61e0252c42d3b421382ba9922","tid":840993,"uid":90787,"like":356,"dislike":4,"score":352,"quote":{"pid":"b7d6ea27f19d16bc806caf6115fd8f5211538261","tid":840993,"uid":58140,"like":2751,"dislike":11,"score":2740,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"我唔撚數啦 直接屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961611c2c29b9de33c2547be51834b9373573aa9","tid":840993,"uid":59898,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\